description: Looking for some advice or perspectives on life?  What Would Mr. West Say will tell you  . . . what Mr. West has said in various interviews that may or may not be applicable to your situation. This skill will let you finish, but it does not know where to find your croissants.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, open What Would Mr. West Say
Alexa, ask What Would Mr. West Say and tell me what would Mr. West say
Alexa, ask What Would Mr. West Say for what would Mr. West do
imageAltText: What Would Mr. West Say icon
name: What Would Mr. West Say
shortDescription: Gives advice uttered by Mr. West.
